<begin $DESCRIPTION>
%package [LABEL]
Group: System Environment/BlueQuartz
Summary: [LABEL] for [VENDOR]-[SERVICE].
[AUTOFILL]
[BUILDARCH]
[PROVIDES]

%description [LABEL]
The [VENDOR]-[SERVICE]-[LABEL] package contains the [LABEL]
information for [VENDOR]-[SERVICE].

<end $DESCRIPTION>

<begin %PREP>
